## API Configuration Template
## Copy this file to 'local.properties' and add your real API keys
## DO NOT commit local.properties to Git (it's in .gitignore for security)

# OpenAI API Key (for Whisper transcription and GPT summaries)
# Get your key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-actual-openai-api-key-here

# Google Gemini API Key (for AI summaries)
# Get your key from: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-actual-gemini-api-key-here

## Instructions:
## 1. Copy this file: cp local.properties.example local.properties
## 2. Edit local.properties and replace the placeholder keys with your real keys
## 3. Save the file
## 4. Build the app: ./gradlew clean assembleDebug

## Security Note:
## - local.properties is git-ignored and will NOT be committed
## - Never share your API keys publicly
## - Never commit API keys to Git
## - If you accidentally expose a key, revoke it immediately and create a new one
